Paladin Capital Says Curro Holdings Plans to List Within `Next Few Months'

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-10T10:38:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/paladin-capital-says-curro-holdings-plans-to-list-within-next-few-months-.html
  Paladin Capital Ltd. (PLD)  said the board
of Curro Holdings Ltd. has decided to proceed with a listing
“within the next few months.”  Paladin is also considering other corporate actions for its
subsidiary, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
